Subject: [PATCH 168/268] arm64: dts: renesas: r8a774b1: PWM support for RZ/G2N

This patch adds PWM device nodes for R8A774B1 SoC.

Signed-off-by: Ky Nguyen <ky.nguyen.uj@renesas.com>
Signed-off-by: Hien Huynh <hien.huynh.px@renesas.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a774b1.dtsi | 70 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 70 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a774b1.dtsi b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a774b1.dtsi
index 241dcdc..b08813a 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a774b1.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a774b1.dtsi
@@ -1255,6 +1255,76 @@
 			#thermal-sensor-cells = <1>;
 			status = "okay";
 		};
+
+		pwm0: pwm@e6e30000 {
+			compatible = "renesas,pwm-r8a774b1", "renesas,pwm-rcar";
